'From Squeak3.7alpha of ''11 September 2003'' [latest update: #5595] on 4 December 2003 at 1:31:24 pm'!"Change Set:		irc-removalDate:			3 December 2003Author:			Marcus DenkerThis changeset IRC from the image.The version of IRC that's now in the image is not used(And may even not work). Please use EnhIRC (from SqueakMap)instead.This does:  -> removes all classes in the category Network-IRC Chat  -> deletes SystemDictionary>>discardIRC  -> unregisteres IRC from the Menu"!SystemDictionary removeSelector: #discardIRC!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #IRCChannelInfo!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #IRCChannelListBrowser!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #IRCChannelObserver!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #IRCChannelSummary!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #IRCChannelUsersBrowser!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #IRCConnection!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #IRCDirectMessagesObserver!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #IRCMessage!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #IRCMessagePattern!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #IRCMessageSet!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #IRCMorph!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #IRCProtocolMessage!Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #IRCRecipientFilter!"Postscript:"SystemOrganization removeCategoriesMatching: 'Network-IRC Chat'.TheWorldMenu unregisterOpenCommand: 'IRC chat'.!